<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200923/dccc4de9eb494d7981a00bc43f97a675.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>5</span><span>0</span><span>X</span></p>
<p><span>三星Galaxy</span><span></span><span>Note</span><span>20 </span><span>Ultra</span><span>5</span><span>G除了支持5倍光学变焦外，还支持5</span><span>0</span><span>倍混合变焦，与上半年的Galaxy</span><span></span><span>S20</span><span></span><span>Ultra一样，Galaxy</span><span></span><span>Note</span><span>20 </span><span>Ultra</span><span>5</span><span>G的5</span><span>0</span><span>倍变焦体验同样顺滑，没有明显的卡顿。而在成像素质上，1</span><span>0</span><span>倍样张看不出明显的噪点，</span><span>20</span><span>倍、5</span><span>0</span><span>倍的样张</span><span>噪点就较为明显，不过与其他手机品牌相比，Galaxy</span><span></span><span>Note</span><span>20 </span><span>Ultra</span><span>5</span><span>G的变焦体验与成像素质可以说是领先的。</span></p>
